# Welcome Page Changelog

`src/Welcome.mdx` contains a versioned changelog. It **must be updated before every commit**.

## Rules

- Before committing, always add or update a changelog entry in `src/Welcome.mdx` under the appropriate version heading.
- If a new version milestone is reached, add a new `### vX.Y — Month YYYY` section above the previous one.
- Each entry should briefly describe what was added, changed, or fixed — one bullet per component/feature.
- Never commit without checking that the changelog reflects the changes in that commit.

## Format

```mdx
### v0.8 — 22 April 2026
- **ComponentName** short description of what was added or changed
- **AnotherThing** short description
```
